              <li><span class="icon do-icon">&#10003;</span> Pat dry with disposable paper products — not cloth towels</li>
              <li><span class="icon do-icon">&#10003;</span> Sleep on a travel pillow to avoid pressure on healing piercings</li>
              <li><span class="icon do-icon">&#10003;</span> Leave jewelry in for the full healing period</li>
              <li><span class="icon do-icon">&#10003;</span> See your piercer if you notice signs of infection (increasing redness, warmth, pus)</li>
